description:
View your available balance, find ATM and Reload locations, or check the status of your Monthly Charge Waiver, all through our secure app.

Getting the most out of your award-winning Green Dot® prepaid debit card has never been easier. Download our FREE app today for on-the-go access to your online account.
    • View transaction history
    • Find ATMs and Reload locations
    • Track your progress toward the Monthly Charge Waiver
  
GET THE MOST OUT OF YOUR GREEN DOT CARD: 
 
RELOADING MADE EASY
Visit a participating retailer to enjoy the simplicity and ease of Reload @ the Register. Just hand the associate your cash, and once your card is swiped, the money is loaded automatically to your card!

Reload fee and limits apply.

CARD BENEFITS:
    • Shop EVERYWHERE Visa or MasterCard prepaid debit cards are accepted in the U.S.
    • Absolutely NO overdraft or penalty fees * 
    • NO minimum balance or credit check to get a card 
    • 24,000 FREE MoneyPass® ATMs * *

* Monthly and other fees apply. 
** At non-MoneyPass ATMs, $2.50 for withdrawals and $0.50 for balance inquiries, plus any ATM owner fees. ATM and cash access available only on personalized cards. So, look for the MoneyPass logo!

Technology Privacy Statement: https://m2.greendot.com/legal/tps 

Terms of Use: https://m2.greendot.com/legal/tos

Green Dot Corp adheres to PCI DSS compliance.
Green Dot Cards are issued by Green Dot Bank, Member, FDIC.


Green Dot Bank operates under the following registered trade names: GoBank, Green Dot Bank and Bonneville Bank. All of these registered trade names are used by, and refer to, a single FDIC-insured bank, Green Dot Bank. Deposits under any of these trade names are deposits with Green Dot Bank and are aggregated for deposit insurance coverage.
